                        <!-- Orders -->
                        <h2 class="title title--small">Orders</h2> 

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">When will you charge my credit card?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>Unlabel will charge your credit card when your order is placed.</p>
                        </div> 

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">When will my order arrive?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>When you purchase an item on Unlabel, you place an order directly with a brand. On <a class="links-faq" href="/">unlabel.us</a>, you can view the estimated shipping time frame for any given product when you click on the “Shipping Info” tab on the product page.</p>

                            <p>When you place an order, you will receive a confirmation email from Unlabel stating you placed an order and then another email with an estimated arrival date and the tracking number associated with your order from the respective brand.</p>
                        </div> 

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">Can I modify my order before it is shipped?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>When you place an order on Unlabel, your order is immediately processed directly with our brand partners who fulfill and ship your orders. Due to the quick workaround time for processing orders, we generally cannot make any modifications to your order, however, please contact <a class="links-faq" href="mailto:support@unlabel.us">support@unlabel.us</a> and a member of our team will try to work with the brand to accommodate your request. Kindly note this is not guaranteed, as some of our brand partners have very short order processing windows to ensure a speedy delivery.</p>
                        </div> 

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">How do I cancel my order?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>Since orders are placed with our brand partners cancellations are subject to each brand's order fulfillment process, so we typically are unable to cancel orders once they have been placed. Don’t worry! If your product is eligible for a return then you will receive a full refund once your return is delivered back to the brand.</p>
                        </div> 

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">Where can I find my order number?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>Once you place an order, You can find all your order information — including your order number — within the confirmation email.</p>
                        </div>

                        <h3 class="subtitle subtitle--small">I placed an order but didn't receive a confirmation email. Did my order go through?</h3>
                        <div>
                            <p>Every time you place an order, you should receive a confirmation email from Unlabel.</p>

                            <p>If you didn’t receive an email, first check your Spam folder. If the confirmation email isn’t there, your order may not have been processed.</p>
                        </div>                                                          
